<front>
<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Albrecht [Fleischmann], Pfarrer zu St. Sebald in Nürnberg</head><p>Der Rat dankt für die Auskünfte und bittet um Neuigkeiten.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_151" id="75v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab facs="#facs_151_r1l1">Meiſter <expan>Albr<ex>echt</ex></expan> Pfarrer </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_151_r1l2">cʒu ſant <expan>Seb<ex>old</ex></expan> cʒu
                                <expan>Nür<ex>emberg</ex></expan>
</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_151_r1l3">Erſamer vnd lieber <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> / Als Jr vns <expan>yecʒ<ex>unden</ex></expan> von <expan>etlıch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> leuffen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_151_r1l4">vnd <expan>ſach<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>verſchrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> habt / Des dancken vvir <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> erſamkeit mit </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_151_r1l7">gancʒem fleiſʒ / <expan>vvan<ex>n</ex></expan> Jr 
<add><ab facs="#facs_151_line_1573112037797_250">habt </ab></add> vns daran beſunder lieb vnd gunſt bevveiſet </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_151_r1l8">
<del rend="strikethrough">habt </del> / Vnd <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan> . daʒ Jr vns beẏ dem gegenvvertigen ~ <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> Poten </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_151_r1l9">aber <expan>verſchreib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vnd cʒuvviſſen tun wöllet ſo Jr eẏgentlicheſt mügt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_151_r1l11">vvie ſich <expan>dıeſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ſache vnd leuffe 
<del rend="strikethrough">angeſlagen </del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_151_line_1586152482224_171">ſıder gemacht </ab></add> <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<add><ab facs="#facs_151_line_1586152486765_176">oder ob eʒ noch alſo ſtee </ab></add> / oder vvie eʒ 
<del rend="strikethrough">noch </del></ab>
<ab facs="#facs_151_r1l12">darümb geſtalt ſeẏ vnd 
<del rend="strikethrough">waʒ </del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_151_line_1573112283446_274">ob </ab></add> Jr auch ſider 
<del rend="strikethrough">fremde </del> icht mer newer </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_151_r1l13">oder fremder leuffe / vnd ſache erfaren oder <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nomen</expan> het / <expan>alſu<ex>er</ex>re</expan> euch </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_151_r1l14">das füglich ſeẏ . Das wöllen etc <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>fe<ex>ri</ex>a</expan> vj̃ <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> <expan>M<ex>isericord</ex>ia</expan>
<del rend="strikethrough"><gap reason="illegible"/></del> <expan>d<expan>omi</expan>nȷ</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_151_r1l16">Anno etc xv<hi rend="sup">to</hi></ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_151" id="75v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Meister <expan>Albr<ex>echt</ex></expan>, pfarrer czu sant
                                <expan>Seb<ex>old</ex></expan> czu <expan>Nür<ex>emberg</ex></expan>
</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Ersamer und lieber <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re,</expan> als ir uns
                                <expan>yecz<ex>unden</ex></expan> von
                            <expan>etlich<ex>e</ex>n</expan> leuffen und
                            <expan>sach<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>verschrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> habt, des dancken wir
                                <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> ersamkeit mit ganczem fleisz,
                                <expan>wan<ex>n</ex></expan> ir <add>habt</add> uns daran besunder
                        lieb und gunst beweiset. Und <expan>ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>, daz ir uns bey
                        dem gegenwertigen <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan> poten aber
                                <expan>verschreib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und czu wissen tun wöllet, so
                        ir eygentlichest mügt, wie sich <expan>dieselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> sache und
                        leuffe <add>sider gemacht</add>
<expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<add>oder ob ez noch also stee</add> oder wie ez darümb gestalt sey und
                            <add>ob</add> ir auch sider icht mer newer oder fremder leuffe und sache
                        erfaren oder <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nomen</expan> het,
                            <expan>alsv<ex>er</ex>re</expan> euch das füglich sey. Das wöllen etc.
                                <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>fe<ex>ri</ex>a</expan> vi <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan>
<expan>m<ex>isericord</ex>ia</expan>
<expan>d<expan>omi</expan>ni</expan> anno etc. xv<hi rend="sup">to</hi>.
                    </ab>
</div>
</div></body>
</text>
